---
title: Beef & Soy Slaw Tacos with Sriracha Mayo & Spring Onion
description: May we introduce your new vegetarian friendly favourite, the beef strips taco. Golden and glowing, the sriracha mayo combo really brings out the best in this dish and goes nicely with slaw, all put together in a warm taco. Delish!
